column5: Q: The Stanley Cup was recently on tour in my town, and I kissed it. Do I have to worry about being infected by listeria?  A: You are safe. The Stanley Cup has not been in contact with any Maple Leaf product in over 40 years.
BWAHAHAHAHAHA!!!!   It's funny because it's true....
